        <item>
            <title>OpenAI 倡通用人工智能 5 大阶段，表示其人工智能即将进入第 2 阶段</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:30:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AGI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1249963</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">根据报道指出，OpenAI 已经开发出了一个能够跟进建立通用人工智能（AGI）发展的系统。OpenAI 向旗下员工展示了一个将人工智能分成五个阶段的系统，有助确认人工智能的进展。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249977 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3-694x390.jpg" alt="OpenAI" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.tomsguide.com/phones/iphones/openai-could-play-a-role-in-apples-ios-18-update-and-that-has-me-worried">Tom&#8217;s Guide</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">OpenAI 将人工智能分成五大等级，分别是聊天机械人（Chatbots）、能解决人类水平问题的推理者（Reasoners）、能够代表用户采取行动的代理（Agents）、能够帮助发明的创新者（Innovator）和能够完成组织工作的组织者（Organizations）。OpenAI 向员工表示目前公司的进展正处于第一阶段，并有望即将达到第二阶段。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249978 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope-694x416.jpg" alt="Sam Altman" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope.jpg 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://beebom.com/sam-altman-returns-openai-ceo-new-board-appointed/">Beebom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">OpenAI 一直致力建构通用人工智能，其提出的五阶段分类系统仍在研究当中，相信会根据得到的反馈意见再进行修改。OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 认为通用人工智能会是人类有史以来创造过最好的工具，他和 OpenAI 技术总监 Mira Murati 在上年十月时曾表示通用人工智能将在未来十年内实现。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.pymnts.com/artificial-intelligence-2/2024/openai-defines-five-steps-from-ai-to-agi/">PYMNTS</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://coingeek.com/openai-faces-probe-in-poland-over-alleged-breach-of-data-protection-rules/">CoinGeek</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/10/microsoft-ditches-openai-board-observer-seat-amid-regulatory-scrutiny/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OpenAI 董事会将不加入企业观察员　Microsoft 和 Apple 双双放弃代表席位</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/amazfit-zepp-os-4-upgrade-gpt-4o-support/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多款 Amazfit 智能手表系统更新，将加入 OpenAI GPT-o 多语言模型支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-to-get-openai-board-observer-role/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传 Apple 高层将加入 OpenAI 董事会　观察员身份并无投票权</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/">OpenAI 倡通用人工智能 5 大阶段，表示其人工智能即将进入第 2 阶段</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
