            <title>【教学】令「从我的 iPhone 传送」消失，教你如何制作个人化电子邮件签名</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/no-more-sent-from-my-iphone-tutorial/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=no-more-sent-from-my-iphone-tutorial</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/no-more-sent-from-my-iphone-tutorial/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 12:00:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone app]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Email]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[教学]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[邮件]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1249080</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">经常会使用 iPhone「邮件」应用程式的人应该都会留意到，每次邮件的尾端都会显示「从我的 iPhone 传送」的字样，相信不少人都会将其删掉。对方知道邮件是从手机发出，可能会有损专业的形象。其实 iPhone 的这个功能算是一个小小的推广广告，并没有什么实际效用，设定中是可以修改这个功能并将预设签名转成你想显示的文字格式。</p><figure id="attachment_1249096" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249096" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249096 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1643-268x580.jpg" alt="Mail" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1643-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1643.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249096" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲iPhone 预设签名</span></figcaption></figure><h2>Step 1</h2><p>打开设定，进入邮件；</p><figure id="attachment_1249084" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249084" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249084 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1636-268x580.jpeg" alt="iPhone" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1636-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1636.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249084" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲进入邮件设定</span></figcaption></figure><h2>Step 2</h2><p>拉至底部的「编写邮件」，会发现可以设定邮件签名；</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249085 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1637-268x580.jpeg" alt="iPhone" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1637-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1637.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2>Step 3</h2><p>将原本的「从我的 iPhone 传送」删除，打上自己想显示的签名即可（你还能自订文字的格式 ）。</p><figure id="attachment_1249086" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249086" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249086 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1639-268x580.jpeg" alt="iPhone" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1639-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1639.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249086" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲可自订文字格式</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249087" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249087" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249087 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1640-268x580.jpeg" alt="iPhone" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1640-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1640.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249087" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲可选粗体、斜体和底线</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249097" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249097 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1644-268x580.jpg" alt="Mail" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1644-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1644.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249097" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲修改完成后的效果</span></figcaption></figure><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.slashgear.com/1368209/how-to-fix-iphone-mail-app-not-receiving-emails/">SlashGear</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/08/how-to-use-gemini-on-ios-and-android-devices/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iPhone 都用到 Gemini　教你如何在 Android 和 iOS 装置上使用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/final-cut-pro-4-iphone-camera/software/ipad-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Final Cut Pro 同时睇多部 iPhone 画面　最多支援 4 部 + 延迟率低</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/19/leica-lux-iphone/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Leica LUX iPhone 手机 App 教学，模拟徕卡镜头 + 拍出原汁原味 Leica Look 相片</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/no-more-sent-from-my-iphone-tutorial/tips-2/">【教学】令「从我的 iPhone 传送」消失，教你如何制作个人化电子邮件签名</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
